column5: Anyone know of any good walleye lakes north of Cabonga Res. in Quebec?We go to Cabonga but they close fishing first week in September. Would like to try further north in middle of September.Thanks>>>

Try the link below and I think with the choices will be able to find a spot. After you have found a few prospects e-mail me and if I know something on your choices I will be glad to help you.http://www.fpq.com
Thanks Nemio, just went to the site and I think this is what I have been looking for. A lot of good information!~
